headline: Compared to Estimates, Essex Property Trust (ESS) Q4 Earnings: A Look at Key Metrics
summary: While the top- and bottom-line numbers for Essex Property Trust (ESS) give a sense of how the business performed in the quarter ended December 2024, it could be worth looking at how some of its key metrics compare to Wall Street estimates and year-ago values.

headline: Essex Property Trust (ESS) Q4 FFO and Revenues Top Estimates
summary: Essex Property Trust (ESS) delivered FFO and revenue surprises of 0.51% and 0.31%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: Essex Property Trust: Q4 Earnings Snapshot
summary: The real estate investment trust, based in San Mateo, California, said it had funds from operations of $261.5 million, or $3.92 per share, in the period. The average estimate of 11 analysts surveyed by Zacks Investment Research was for funds from operations of $3.90 per share. Funds from operations is a closely watched measure in the REIT industry.

headline: Essex Announces Fourth Quarter and Full-Year 2024 Results and Provides 2025 Guidance
summary: SAN MATEO, Calif., February 04, 2025--Essex Property Trust, Inc. (NYSE:ESS) (the "Company") announced today its fourth quarter and full-year 2024 earnings results and related business activities.
